org.zaproxy.zap.spider.filters
Class FetchFilter

java.lang.Object
  org.zaproxy.zap.spider.filters.FetchFilter
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultFetchFilter
public abstract class FetchFilter
extends java.lang.Object

A FetchFilter is used to filter which resources should be fetched and processed by the Spider and which shouldn't. This filter is applied before adding the resource in the processing queue.

Nested Class Summary
static class FetchFilter.FetchStatus
          The FetchStatus enum is used as the status returned by a FetchFilter, stating if the uri is accepted or, if not, why was it not accepted.
